          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Bureau Guidance Transparency Act - Amends the Consumer Financial Protection Act of 2010 to direct the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau (CFPB), before issuing any guidance, to: (1) provide for a public notice and comment period before issuing the guidance in final form; and (2) make available to the public, when issuing guidance in final form, all studies, data, and other analysis relied upon by the CFPB in preparing and issuing such guidance.</p>]]></text>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2014-07-23T21:29:38Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDate>2014-05-20</actionDate>
          <updateDate>2014-05-20T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
    </summaries>
